Norcal Regional Championship

Overview

Qualifications
Our robot worked effectively during qualifications, and we won 5 out of our 6 matches, seeding 2nd in the Tule Elk division.

Eliminations
During alliance selections, we declined Team 6002, Basilisks' (the first seed) invitation and formed our own alliance with the Roboknights (Team 5220) and the Tino 49ers (Team 4950). We went 2-0 in semifinals, advancing to finals, where we lost 0-2 to the first seed alliance. We learned that our robot was susceptible to defense, and Team 5326, the Enterprisers, took advantage of this to defeat us in finals.
In semi-finals, we set a NorCal high score of 585 points.

Awards

  • Division Finalist Captain
